Hey Brian!  How are you?  Hope all is going well 

Do you happen to know anyone in the Phoenix/Scottsdale area that can help me with my iPhone/iTunes?  I had an issue with my MacBook and had to reinstall my operating system. The bad part is that I didn't get a chance to backup the music that was on iTunes.  Do you know anyone that can help me transfer my music from my phone back to my computer so I don't lose it all?


Thanks,
Andrew

Brian
I am not sure. The geniui at the apple store should be able to help. I have been great. Just got married a few months ago to an awesomr polish woman. Bought a house in scottsdale just before that. We should meet up for tea sometime.

Thanks, I tried that, but they can't really give advice on that cause there legal and licensing issues with that. The guy just told me to Google it and I should be able to find something.

That's great to hear about your wedding!  Congrats and yeah, maybe we can meet up one day
